        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2797059211" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5471726210211882296"><b>Note: This was originally written on 10/7/2009</b> I began reading this book not expecting much, but I was delightfully surprised to find it is one of the best I have read in a very long time. It is, of course, about romance and delicious food. But it is also about history, for as it turns out most of the events and incidents described in this book actually took place.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


