              <span id="reviewTextContainer68887235" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13512230935297433912">Overall I would recommend this as a light read, though it got a bit far-fetched at times. It is about 50% love story, 25% war story, 25% food story. I guess I would categorize it as historical fiction, because it all takes place in Naples during WWII. Though the events are all based on true events, the fact that so many things happened to the main characters is where it gets a bit far-fetched feeling at times. However, if you like historic fiction and don&apos;t want anything too heavy, this is perfe</span>
  <span id="freeText13512230935297433912" style="display:none">Overall I would recommend this as a light read, though it got a bit far-fetched at times. It is about 50% love story, 25% war story, 25% food story. I guess I would categorize it as historical fiction, because it all takes place in Naples during WWII. Though the events are all based on true events, the fact that so many things happened to the main characters is where it gets a bit far-fetched feeling at times. However, if you like historic fiction and don't want anything too heavy, this is perfect.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13512230935297433912" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


